Once in the jungle there was a lion who was moving in search of a prey. 
But there was a hunter's net. The hunter throw the net towrds him. The lion could not come out of the net. 
A mouse was coming from the jungle, he saw the lion and the lion told the mouse to save him. But the mouse said that 
you was coming to kill me, why do I help you. Then the lion realised that we should not kill anyone. And after that the mouse cut the net and saved 
the lion. 